248
00:22:46,677 --> 00:22:48,778
Awak kata ada benda penting nak cakap dengan saya.

249
00:22:49,056 --> 00:22:49,696
Ya.

250
00:22:50,261 --> 00:22:51,706
Saya langsung tak rasa tenang.

251
00:22:51,957 --> 00:22:52,997
Jadi saya nak minta maaf

252
00:22:53,226 --> 00:22:54,512
sebab melampaui batas.

253
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:17,413
Tak apa, betul.

254
00:23:18,314 --> 00:23:19,200
Terima kasih.

255
00:23:41,861 --> 00:23:43,061
Jom kita jalan-jalan?

256
00:24:12,752 --> 00:24:13,984
Cantik sangat kat sini.

257
00:24:18,997 --> 00:24:20,460
Petang nanti lagi cantik.

258
00:24:24,762 --> 00:24:26,021
Lain kali,

259
00:24:26,746 --> 00:24:27,866
awak nak datang sini dengan saya lagi?

260
00:24:37,104 --> 00:24:37,941
Awak...

261
00:24:38,549 --> 00:24:39,856
tak nak ikut saya?

262
00:24:52,981 --> 00:24:53,712
Awak nak datang?

263
00:25:13,210 --> 00:25:18,085
Tentang yang saya nak cakap—awak mungkin tertanya kenapa saya cium awak.

264
00:25:20,565 --> 00:25:21,962
Jawapannya,

265
00:25:22,298 --> 00:25:23,600
sebab saya memang nak cium awak.

266
00:25:25,600 --> 00:25:26,954
Bukan semalam saja.

267
00:25:28,021 --> 00:25:29,152
Sekarang pun sama.

268
00:25:32,293 --> 00:25:33,834
Saya nak hargai awak,

269
00:25:35,061 --> 00:25:36,522
bukan dalam surat saja.

270
00:25:41,013 --> 00:25:42,826
Saya nak dengar awak panggil nama saya,

271
00:25:43,424 --> 00:25:44,784
dan cakap awak sayang saya.

272
00:25:48,112 --> 00:25:50,460
Bukan sekadar beri semangat dari jauh.

273
00:25:55,920 --> 00:25:57,344
Saya nak peluk awak,

274
00:25:58,362 --> 00:25:59,813
dan jaga awak sebaik mungkin

275
00:26:00,800 --> 00:26:02,460
sebagai seorang lelaki mampu.

276
00:26:07,813 --> 00:26:08,880
Saya sayang awak.

277
00:26:23,818 --> 00:26:25,546
Mulai sekarang, sepanjang hidup saya.

278
00:26:47,872 --> 00:26:50,080
Tolong jadi teman lelaki saya.

279
00:27:26,874 --> 00:27:30,224
Kalau awak tahu siapa saya sebenarnya, awak tak kecewa, kan?

280
00:27:30,736 --> 00:27:31,765
Tak mungkin.

281
00:27:32,021 --> 00:27:33,285
Jadi diri awak pun dah cukup.

282
00:27:33,616 --> 00:27:34,864
Tak ada siapa boleh lebih baik dari ini.

283
00:27:40,368 --> 00:27:41,493
Saya minta maaf.

284
00:27:42,042 --> 00:27:43,978
Maaf sebab cuba tarik awak keluar dari zon selamat awak.

285
00:27:45,242 --> 00:27:48,762
Tapi lepas ni, boleh saya jadi zon selamat awak juga?

286
00:27:54,768 --> 00:27:56,266
Ini mungkin terlalu cepat.

287
00:27:58,389 --> 00:27:59,898
Jadi macam mana kalau begini?

288
00:28:01,200 --> 00:28:02,634
Aku akan kira dari satu sampai sepuluh.

289
00:28:03,594 --> 00:28:05,386
Soalan yang aku tanya tadi—

290
00:28:06,266 --> 00:28:07,776
kalau kau belum bersedia,

291
00:28:08,460 --> 00:28:09,861
kau boleh pergi saja.

292
00:28:10,613 --> 00:28:12,261
Dan kita kembali macam dulu,

293
00:28:13,205 --> 00:28:14,650
tempat yang buat kau rasa selesa.

294
00:28:15,125 --> 00:28:16,661
Walau selama mana pun, aku akan tunggu.

295
00:28:19,056 --> 00:28:20,725
Tapi kalau kau kata ya,

296
00:28:22,101 --> 00:28:23,872
boleh tolong pusing balik?

297
00:28:29,552 --> 00:28:30,460
Sepuluh.

298
00:28:32,314 --> 00:28:33,248
Sembilan.

299
00:28:34,394 --> 00:28:35,530
Lapan.

300
00:28:36,981 --> 00:28:37,722
Tujuh.

301
00:28:38,869 --> 00:28:39,696
Enam.

302
00:28:43,029 --> 00:28:44,042
Lima.

303
00:28:49,210 --> 00:28:50,341
Empat.

304
00:28:56,885 --> 00:28:57,754
Tiga.

305
00:29:03,157 --> 00:29:04,128
Dua.

306
00:29:14,460 --> 00:29:15,237
Satu.

307
00:29:35,722 --> 00:29:36,624
Ya.

308
00:30:06,954 --> 00:30:08,256
Akhirnya dapat jumpa awak.

309
00:30:09,072 --> 00:30:10,410
Orang dari surat-surat itu.

310
00:30:11,152 --> 00:30:12,074
Sama juga.

311
00:30:15,360 --> 00:30:16,960
Sebagai orang dari surat-surat itu.

312
00:30:18,170 --> 00:30:19,968
Ini kali pertama aku dengar suara kau.

313
00:30:20,629 --> 00:30:22,357
Nak perkenalkan diri?

314
00:30:29,877 --> 00:30:30,901
Typhoon.

315
00:30:32,170 --> 00:30:33,333
Dan kau?

316
00:30:34,261 --> 00:30:35,578
Tonfah.

317
00:30:37,440 --> 00:30:39,253
Gembira dapat sayang awak.

318
00:30:43,824 --> 00:30:46,405
Aku pun gembira dapat sayang kau.

319
00:31:03,114 --> 00:31:03,760
Phoon.

320
00:31:05,456 --> 00:31:08,037
P'Fah menipu. Aku tak sempat bersedia pun.

321
00:31:09,248 --> 00:31:11,024
Boleh aku post di Instagram dan tag kau?

322
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:13,706
Boleh, ya?

323
00:31:14,064 --> 00:31:16,901
Hei, kita dah bercinta. Tak boleh post gambar couple?

324
00:31:19,429 --> 00:31:20,725
Baiklah.

325
00:31:23,493 --> 00:31:24,400
Oh.

326
00:31:26,170 --> 00:31:28,128
P'Fah pun ada Instagram aku?

327
00:31:29,296 --> 00:31:31,893
Ya. Aku selalu juga tengok.

328
00:31:33,077 --> 00:31:33,856
Phoon.

329
00:31:34,213 --> 00:31:36,677
Tunggu sekejap. Nanti kau sesat.

330
00:31:38,506 --> 00:31:39,653
Aku takkan sesat.

331
00:31:40,341 --> 00:31:41,056
Betul?

332
00:31:41,866 --> 00:31:43,632
Jadi aku dah tak diperlukan?

333
00:31:44,789 --> 00:31:48,362
Eh—tak. Bukan itu maksud aku.

334
00:31:51,658 --> 00:31:52,460
Dan ini—

335
00:31:53,002 --> 00:31:53,850
macam mana kau sampai sini?

336
00:31:55,146 --> 00:31:56,357
Err—

337
00:31:57,024 --> 00:31:57,957
Aku panggil kereta.

338
00:32:00,309 --> 00:32:01,296
Jadi—

339
00:32:02,266 --> 00:32:03,610
nak balik dengan aku?

340
00:32:05,082 --> 00:32:07,946
Maksudnya kau hantar aku balik asrama?

341
00:32:11,408 --> 00:32:12,602
Betul?

342
00:32:13,946 --> 00:32:15,690
Tak boleh ke kau tidur di rumah aku?

343
00:32:15,909 --> 00:32:17,413
Kita dah bercinta sekarang.

344
00:32:19,296 --> 00:32:22,256
Jadi kalau ya pun kenapa?

345
00:32:24,074 --> 00:32:26,460
Jadi kita patut luangkan masa bersama.

346
00:32:26,938 --> 00:32:28,090
Apa yang kau fikir, Phoon?

347
00:32:28,986 --> 00:32:29,626
Hmm?

348
00:32:30,666 --> 00:32:31,152
Hmm?

349
00:32:33,328 --> 00:32:35,168
Aku tak fikir apa-apa pun.

350
00:32:36,325 --> 00:32:37,594
- Jom.
- Hei.

351
00:32:38,106 --> 00:32:39,386
Kau betul-betul tak nak ikut?

352
00:32:39,664 --> 00:32:42,048
- Tak.
- Katil aku selesa sangat.

353
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:44,165
Phoon, tunggu aku.

354
00:33:11,829 --> 00:33:14,218
Aku ingat aku takkan kembali sini lagi.

355
00:33:14,944 --> 00:33:16,352
Kau memang kena kembali.

356
00:33:16,693 --> 00:33:18,149
Ke mana pun kau pergi,

357
00:33:18,394 --> 00:33:19,962
kau tetap kena balik pada P'Fah.

358
00:33:24,650 --> 00:33:25,546
Oh ya—

359
00:33:26,794 --> 00:33:28,460
kenapa kau pusing balik?

360
00:33:30,042 --> 00:33:31,349
Aku ingat—

361
00:33:32,282 --> 00:33:33,712
kau nak pergi begitu saja.

362
00:33:35,365 --> 00:33:36,346
Tak.

363
00:33:37,514 --> 00:33:38,954
Aku sentiasa ada di sini.

364
00:33:40,698 --> 00:33:42,010
Aku janji pada diri sendiri

365
00:33:42,602 --> 00:33:44,277
sejak hari aku tinggalkan tempat ini.

366
00:33:45,605 --> 00:33:47,002
aku takkan pergi mana-mana.

367
00:33:47,632 --> 00:33:49,344
Kalau kau pusing balik,

368
00:33:50,261 --> 00:33:51,648
aku akan sentiasa ada di sini.

369
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:58,944
Mari sini, budak baik.

370
00:33:59,333 --> 00:34:01,754
Kenapa dulu kau kata aku menyusahkan kau?

371
00:34:05,882 --> 00:34:07,722
Kau nak pergi mana?

372
00:34:10,410 --> 00:34:12,112
P'Fah, lepaskan.

373
00:34:12,602 --> 00:34:13,541
Tak nak.

374
00:34:14,032 --> 00:34:17,536
Supaya aku tahu kau tipu aku atau tak.

375
00:34:20,597 --> 00:34:21,909
Aku tak menipu.

376
00:34:23,093 --> 00:34:24,160
Betul?

377
00:34:25,792 --> 00:34:28,069
Budak nakal kena dihukum.

378
00:34:28,460 --> 00:34:29,034
Eh—

379
00:34:29,605 --> 00:34:31,301
Aku belum boleh beritahu kau lagi.

380
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:32,460
Tentang—

381
00:34:32,757 --> 00:34:34,357
kenapa aku terpaksa buat begitu.

382
00:34:39,162 --> 00:34:40,730
Jadi ada sebab, tapi tak boleh cakap?

383
00:34:42,460 --> 00:34:43,605
Maaf.

384
00:34:45,850 --> 00:34:47,109
Kalau macam tu, tak apa.

385
00:34:48,624 --> 00:34:49,552
Aku rasa—

386
00:34:51,402 --> 00:34:52,976
kita patut tukar permohonan maaf kau

387
00:34:53,904 --> 00:34:55,557
jadi benda lain.

388
00:34:59,797 --> 00:35:01,104
P'Fah nak—

389
00:35:02,208 --> 00:35:02,922
biar—

390
00:35:03,194 --> 00:35:06,192
tukar maaf itu jadi apa?

391
00:35:48,624 --> 00:35:50,005
Apa kau buat, P'Fah?

392
00:35:50,768 --> 00:35:51,978
Kita simpan dulu untuk nanti.

393
00:35:52,460 --> 00:35:54,245
Aku tahu kau belum bersedia lagi.

394
00:36:00,074 --> 00:36:01,418
Jangan pergi dulu.

395
00:36:02,026 --> 00:36:04,181
Kalau budak baik, duduk macam ni dulu.

396
00:36:07,557 --> 00:36:08,314
Okey.

397
00:36:12,106 --> 00:36:12,960
Kau wangi.

398
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,288
Itu geli.

399
00:36:21,162 --> 00:36:21,898
Phoon.

400
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:25,685
Tak ada apa-apa yang kau nak tanya aku?

401
00:36:31,880 --> 00:36:36,144
P'Fah tak terkejut ke orang dari surat itu Phoon?

402
00:36:42,240 --> 00:36:43,477
Sejujurnya—

403
00:36:44,106 --> 00:36:46,176
aku dah tahu itu kau, Phoon.

404
00:36:46,544 --> 00:36:47,098
Hah?

405
00:36:47,968 --> 00:36:49,754
Macam mana kau tahu? Bila?

406
00:36:50,069 --> 00:36:51,173
Masa hari jadi aku.

407
00:36:52,037 --> 00:36:53,738
Masa kau tulis ucapan hari jadi itu.

408
00:36:54,288 --> 00:36:56,618
Tulisan tangan pada kad dan surat-surat itu—

409
00:36:57,562 --> 00:36:58,460
sama.

410
00:37:01,402 --> 00:37:02,384
Oh.

411
00:37:03,584 --> 00:37:05,488
Jadi aku tersilap, ya?

412
00:37:07,797 --> 00:37:11,034
Jadi bila kau bagi aku baca surat itu, maksudnya—

413
00:37:11,173 --> 00:37:13,669
kau tulis sendiri dan kau baca sendiri.

414
00:37:14,352 --> 00:37:15,962
Aku siap fikir—

415
00:37:16,325 --> 00:37:17,504
comelnya.

416
00:37:18,165 --> 00:37:20,336
P'Fah, kenapa kau usik aku macam tu?

417
00:37:20,410 --> 00:37:22,208
Habis tu, kenapa kau pandai sangat jadi comel?

418
00:37:23,488 --> 00:37:24,544
Aku tak tahu.

419
00:37:25,274 --> 00:37:26,074
Aku...

420
00:37:27,072 --> 00:37:28,336
Aku patut pergi mandi.

421
00:37:29,888 --> 00:37:31,525
Kau selalu lari bila kau malu?

422
00:37:47,392 --> 00:37:48,394
Kau buat apa?

423
00:37:50,922 --> 00:37:52,656
Aku tengok gambar-gambar ni.

424
00:37:54,138 --> 00:37:56,256
Ramai orang hantar benda pada kau.

425
00:37:56,698 --> 00:38:00,394
Tapi kenapa kau pilih balas surat ini?

426
00:38:02,224 --> 00:38:03,760
Sebab surat ini—

427
00:38:04,288 --> 00:38:06,069
dia penuh perhatian,

428
00:38:06,650 --> 00:38:09,349
ikhlas, dan mengambil berat.

429
00:38:11,728 --> 00:38:13,674
Dan tak harap apa-apa balasan.

430
00:38:14,698 --> 00:38:17,216
Macam kau cuma nak aku tahu kau suka aku.

431
00:38:19,002 --> 00:38:19,909
Lagi pun—

432
00:38:21,024 --> 00:38:22,928
ada seseorang dalamnya yang ikut cita rasa aku.

433
00:38:26,208 --> 00:38:28,261
Seseorang yang ikut cita rasa kau?

434
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:32,805
Kau memang ikut cita rasa aku, Phoon.

435
00:38:38,848 --> 00:38:40,357
Saya pun sangat suka awak, P'Fah.

436
00:38:42,460 --> 00:38:43,514
Dari dulu lagi.

437
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:01,621
Nak lari ke mana?

438
00:39:02,757 --> 00:39:04,842
Saya mengantuk.

439
00:39:06,016 --> 00:39:07,354
Duduk dulu, borak dengan saya.

440
00:39:16,234 --> 00:39:18,314
Saya tak percaya ini betul-betul nyata.

441
00:39:20,720 --> 00:39:21,957
Esok...

442
00:39:22,517 --> 00:39:24,272
awak takkan hilang, kan?

443
00:39:26,213 --> 00:39:27,328
Tak mungkin.

444
00:39:28,460 --> 00:39:29,669
Awak pun sama.

445
00:39:32,021 --> 00:39:33,722
Awak takkan hilang lagi, kan?

446
00:39:35,541 --> 00:39:36,698
Saya takkan pergi mana-mana.

447
00:39:37,568 --> 00:39:40,741
Jadi malam ni kita kena peluk erat.

448
00:39:41,173 --> 00:39:43,733
Supaya budak ni tak menyelinap pergi lagi.

449
00:39:45,194 --> 00:39:46,992
Dah cakap, saya tak pergi mana-mana.

450
00:39:49,477 --> 00:39:50,293
Okey.

451
00:39:50,581 --> 00:39:51,733
Saya percaya awak.

452
00:39:52,565 --> 00:39:54,746
Jadi, nak tidur?

453
00:40:06,528 --> 00:40:07,445
Phoon.

454
00:40:10,186 --> 00:40:11,738
Boleh tutup lampu?

455
00:40:16,874 --> 00:40:17,781
Boleh.

456
00:40:19,696 --> 00:40:20,890
Awak dah tak takut?

457
00:40:22,240 --> 00:40:24,757
Kalau awak ada, saya tak takut.

458
00:40:26,592 --> 00:40:27,338
Bagus.

459
00:40:50,954 --> 00:40:51,882
Selamat malam.

460
00:40:55,568 --> 00:40:56,460
Selamat malam.

461
00:41:42,864 --> 00:41:46,773
Selamat pagi, P'Fah. Saya nampak ada makanan
di dapur, jadi saya ingat nak...

462
00:42:08,917 --> 00:42:12,330
Saya dah cakap saya takkan hilang.

463
00:42:13,205 --> 00:42:15,104
Maaf.

464
00:42:15,290 --> 00:42:18,074
Saya bangun tak jumpa awak, terus panik.

465
00:42:19,797 --> 00:42:22,026
Saya cuma nak buat sarapan untuk awak.

466
00:42:24,522 --> 00:42:25,594
Ini...

467
00:42:25,792 --> 00:42:28,405
sandwic dan susu yang awak selalu hantar dulu.

468
00:42:30,218 --> 00:42:31,820
Tapi nampaknya...

469
00:42:32,405 --> 00:42:34,698
P'Arthit yang lebih kerap makan.

470
00:42:34,917 --> 00:42:36,378
Betul.

471
00:42:38,080 --> 00:42:39,642
Tangan saya penuh.

472
00:42:40,101 --> 00:42:41,514
Boleh suapkan saya?

473
00:42:56,992 --> 00:42:59,381
Mmm, sedap sangat.

474
00:43:04,912 --> 00:43:05,546
Oh...

475
00:43:06,768 --> 00:43:10,341
Saya dah beritahu mak ayah saya nak bawa awak datang.

476
00:43:12,460 --> 00:43:14,821
Pak Cik dan Mak Cik tak syak ke?

477
00:43:15,088 --> 00:43:15,600
Tentang...

478
00:43:15,936 --> 00:43:17,621
kenapa saya tiba-tiba datang jumpa mereka?

479
00:43:18,256 --> 00:43:19,136
Tak.

480
00:43:19,386 --> 00:43:21,850
Sejak saya cakap awak belajar sini,

481
00:43:22,341 --> 00:43:24,528
mereka dah banyak kali nak awak datang.

482
00:43:26,768 --> 00:43:27,877
Sebenarnya,

483
00:43:28,416 --> 00:43:30,032
saya patut luang masa datang lebih kerap.

484
00:43:30,602 --> 00:43:33,173
Dulu Pak Cik dan Mak Cik baik dengan saya,
dan Fun juga...

485
00:43:41,392 --> 00:43:44,229
Saya pergi ambil susu lagi.

486
00:43:46,352 --> 00:43:49,925
- P'Fah nak apa-apa lagi?
- Tak, saya okey.

487
00:44:51,450 --> 00:44:52,826
Dah sampai, sayang?

488
00:44:54,200 --> 00:44:57,296
Phoon, lama betul Mak Cik tak jumpa kamu.

489
00:44:58,352 --> 00:44:59,712
- Hai, Mak Cik.
- Hai.

490
00:45:00,053 --> 00:45:01,514
Apa khabar? Sihat?

491
00:45:01,909 --> 00:45:04,768
- Saya sihat. Mak Cik?
- Mak Cik pun sihat.

492
00:45:05,360 --> 00:45:07,280
Mak Cik dengar kamu belajar tempat sama dengan Fah, ya?

493
00:45:07,514 --> 00:45:08,352
Ya.

494
00:45:09,130 --> 00:45:12,976
Kenapa tak selalu datang? Kami rindu sangat.

495
00:45:13,200 --> 00:45:16,384
Mak Cik pun dah lama tak berbual dengan Rit.

496
00:45:17,008 --> 00:45:21,738
Uh... maaf.

497
00:45:22,122 --> 00:45:23,365
Mak Cik cuma mengusik.

498
00:45:23,685 --> 00:45:25,664
Mak Cik tahu kamu sibuk belajar.

499
00:45:25,850 --> 00:45:29,642
Dan sekarang kamu tinggal jauh dari rumah, kan?

500
00:45:30,373 --> 00:45:32,122
Jom masuk dulu, sayang. Mari.

501
00:45:49,509 --> 00:45:51,498
Uh, Pak Cik macam mana?

502
00:45:51,738 --> 00:45:55,829
Dia di hospital, sayang. Tapi dia kata dia akan cepat balik
supaya kita boleh makan malam sama-sama.

503
00:45:56,320 --> 00:45:57,978
Dia masih kerja kuat macam biasa, ya?

504
00:45:58,309 --> 00:46:00,304
Tak boleh nak buat apa.

505
00:46:05,493 --> 00:46:09,674
Puan, klien telefon. Mereka tunggu di talian sekarang.

506
00:46:10,890 --> 00:46:13,872
Nampak? Mak Cik belum habis cakap pun.

507
00:46:14,090 --> 00:46:16,229
Baiklah, Mak Cik keluar sekejap angkat telefon.

508
00:46:16,736 --> 00:46:18,224
Fah, tolong tengokkan dia, ya?

509
00:46:18,688 --> 00:46:19,530
Ya, mak.

510
00:46:24,069 --> 00:46:26,282
Mak awak tak berubah langsung, kan?

511
00:46:27,130 --> 00:46:28,037
Betul.

512
00:47:01,850 --> 00:47:03,173
Ini bilik P'Fah.

513
00:47:04,794 --> 00:47:06,288
Lagi besar daripada rumah lama.

514
00:47:08,869 --> 00:47:09,893
Mm.

515
00:47:11,013 --> 00:47:13,306
Tapi tanpa budak-budak jiran datang main...

516
00:47:13,610 --> 00:47:14,762
rasa sunyi sikit.

517
00:47:24,960 --> 00:47:27,493
Awak masih belum tebus sebab lepaskan tangan P'Fah dulu.

518
00:47:29,098 --> 00:47:30,682
Ini rumah awak.

519
00:47:31,072 --> 00:47:33,632
- Kita tak boleh pegang tangan.
- Kenapa?

520
00:47:35,125 --> 00:47:35,466
Sebab...

521
00:47:36,460 --> 00:47:38,576
Kalau orang nampak macam mana?

522
00:47:39,989 --> 00:47:41,514
Phoon, awak tak nak orang lain tahu?

523
00:47:41,770 --> 00:47:42,154
Hmm?

524
00:47:44,101 --> 00:47:46,704
Saya risau Pak Cik dan Mak Cik nampak, nanti tak setuju.

525
00:47:56,736 --> 00:47:57,616
Maaf.

526
00:48:03,584 --> 00:48:05,285
Phoon tak nak lepaskan tangan saya.

527
00:48:05,648 --> 00:48:07,909
Saya akan beritahu mak ayah kita bercinta.

528
00:48:10,602 --> 00:48:13,530
- Tapi...
- Memang kita bercinta.

529
00:48:16,154 --> 00:48:16,810
Okey?

530
00:48:19,722 --> 00:48:20,378
Okey.

531
00:48:31,706 --> 00:48:32,917
Leganya.

532
00:48:39,077 --> 00:48:41,344
Typhoon, lama tak jumpa. Apa khabar?

533
00:48:42,405 --> 00:48:43,328
Saya sihat.

534
00:48:44,154 --> 00:48:45,845
Rit pula? Dia sihat?

535
00:48:51,562 --> 00:48:52,746
Ayah...

536
00:48:54,042 --> 00:48:54,981
sihat.

537
00:48:56,549 --> 00:48:59,178
Hari tu dia kata nak datang, tapi tak datang pun.

538
00:49:08,101 --> 00:49:09,669
- Phoon, sayang.
- Ya?

539
00:49:11,504 --> 00:49:15,130
Makan banyak-banyak, ya? Lama kita tak jumpa.

540
00:49:15,397 --> 00:49:18,080
Kenapa kamu masih kecil macam ni? Mak Cik tak boleh terima.

541
00:49:18,460 --> 00:49:18,986
Ya.

542
00:49:19,797 --> 00:49:20,778
Fah.

543
00:49:21,360 --> 00:49:21,770
Ya?

544
00:49:21,861 --> 00:49:24,848
Mak dengar Hill dan Johan dah ada kekasih. Betul ke?

545
00:49:26,037 --> 00:49:26,992
Ya, mak.

546
00:49:27,445 --> 00:49:28,330
Kamu pula, Fah?

547
00:49:28,677 --> 00:49:31,114
Bila nak carikan mak menantu perempuan?

548
00:49:35,226 --> 00:49:36,949
Anak kita terlalu sibuk belajar.

549
00:49:37,104 --> 00:49:38,320
Oh, ayah.

550
00:49:38,533 --> 00:49:40,460
Takkan tak ada orang untuk dia berbual?

551
00:49:41,450 --> 00:49:43,664
Atau habiskan belajar dulu?

552
00:49:44,170 --> 00:49:44,858
Macam mana, nak?

553
00:50:08,133 --> 00:50:09,760
Ayah. Mak.

554
00:50:12,760 --> 00:50:14,261
Saya dan Phoon sedang bercinta.

555
00:50:30,460 --> 00:50:31,360
Betul ke?

556
00:50:49,706 --> 00:50:53,808
Alamak, bila mak kata nak menantu perempuan,

557
00:50:54,261 --> 00:50:57,717
mak tak sangka cepat sangat jadi.

558
00:50:59,317 --> 00:51:00,460
Ayah, ayah okey?

559
00:51:03,509 --> 00:51:04,304
Mestilah.

560
00:51:05,610 --> 00:51:07,306
Ayah bukan kolot sangat.

561
00:51:09,104 --> 00:51:11,397
Lagi bagus sebab orang yang kita dah kenal.

562
00:51:12,154 --> 00:51:13,776
Jadi kita tak perlu risau

563
00:51:13,824 --> 00:51:15,365
Fah tersalah pilih orang.

564
00:51:19,408 --> 00:51:20,661
Terima kasih.

565
00:51:21,877 --> 00:51:23,557
Dah berapa lama kamu berdua bersama?

566
00:51:26,613 --> 00:51:29,504
Tak lama sangat.

567
00:51:30,757 --> 00:51:33,888
Ini berita baik. Kita patut raikan.

568
00:51:33,957 --> 00:51:35,098
Memang patut kita raikan.

569
00:51:35,264 --> 00:51:35,893
Ya.

570
00:51:36,005 --> 00:51:36,602
Phoon.

571
00:51:37,285 --> 00:51:39,733
- Nak makan apa-apa lagi?
- Tak apa, terima kasih.

572
00:51:40,266 --> 00:51:41,306
Nah, makan.

573
00:51:42,229 --> 00:51:43,333
Kita order dari restoran ni lagi?

574
00:51:43,536 --> 00:51:44,460
Boleh, ayah.

575
00:51:46,630 --> 00:51:47,989
Makan banyak-banyak, ya?

576
00:52:04,090 --> 00:52:05,098
Tengok apa tu?

577
00:52:06,394 --> 00:52:07,578
Easter dan North.

578
00:52:07,936 --> 00:52:09,205
Mereka hantar gambar tunjuk trip luar negara.

579
00:52:09,834 --> 00:52:10,906
Mm.

580
00:52:15,290 --> 00:52:16,650
Phoon, awak nak pergi juga?

581
00:52:18,048 --> 00:52:18,460
Hmm?

582
00:52:23,792 --> 00:52:26,112
Kalau nak pergi, boleh pergi macam tu saja?

583
00:52:29,546 --> 00:52:32,336
Kalau nak pergi, P'Fah akan bawa.

584
00:52:35,322 --> 00:52:36,965
Jangan manjakan aku sangat.

585
00:52:37,552 --> 00:52:38,997
Nanti aku jadi budak manja.

586
00:52:39,541 --> 00:52:40,709
Mm.

587
00:52:41,856 --> 00:52:43,856
Aku memang selalu manjakan teman lelaki aku.

588
00:52:45,637 --> 00:52:46,778
Mm.

589
00:52:48,672 --> 00:52:50,090
Biar aku fikir dulu.

590
00:52:50,554 --> 00:52:53,450
Tapi sekarang, aku tak nak pergi mana-mana.

591
00:52:54,208 --> 00:52:55,680
Kalau bilik P'Fah?

592
00:52:56,325 --> 00:52:57,072
Nak pergi?

593
00:53:00,192 --> 00:53:01,168
Gurau saja.

594
00:53:02,789 --> 00:53:03,546
Oh ya—

595
00:53:05,232 --> 00:53:06,608
Dah rasa lebih baik?

596
00:53:07,434 --> 00:53:09,424
Mak ayah aku macam tak marah pun.

597
00:53:09,898 --> 00:53:11,258
Mereka siap nampak gembira.

598
00:53:12,325 --> 00:53:13,578
Mereka masih baik macam dulu.

599
00:53:21,205 --> 00:53:22,757
Hari ni hari yang baik untuk Phoon?

600
00:53:26,197 --> 00:53:26,677
Ya.

601
00:53:27,680 --> 00:53:29,866
Jadi, hari ni hari yang baik untuk P'Fah?

602
00:53:31,610 --> 00:53:32,874
Dengan Phoon ada di sini.

603
00:53:33,562 --> 00:53:35,200
Mestilah hari ni jadi hari yang baik.

604
00:54:43,664 --> 00:54:45,141
P'Fah.

605
00:54:55,728 --> 00:54:57,600
Aku dah mula hilang sabar.

606
00:55:01,728 --> 00:55:03,829
Tapi aku akan tunggu sampai Phoon bersedia.

607
00:55:11,077 --> 00:55:12,080
Boleh?

608
00:55:34,240 --> 00:55:35,056
Phoon.

609
00:55:37,269 --> 00:55:37,856
Ya.

610
00:55:38,917 --> 00:55:40,405
Kau dah tak keseorangan lagi, tahu.

611
00:55:43,338 --> 00:55:45,669
Benda berat yang kau tanggung tu—

612
00:55:47,386 --> 00:55:48,730
kau boleh kongsi dengan aku.

613
00:55:57,568 --> 00:55:58,613
Faham?

614
00:55:59,317 --> 00:55:59,872
Hmm?

615
00:56:00,410 --> 00:56:01,333
Faham?

616
00:56:01,701 --> 00:56:02,266
Ya.

617
00:56:05,728 --> 00:56:07,098
Tentang yang Khun Tonfah suruh saya siasat,

618
00:56:07,285 --> 00:56:08,928
ada perkembangan untuk saya laporkan.

619
00:56:09,898 --> 00:56:10,597
Teruskan.

620
00:56:11,413 --> 00:56:13,930
Thorfun meninggal dunia tiga hingga empat tahun lepas.

621
00:56:27,962 --> 00:56:29,573
Oh, awal Phoon bangun.

622
00:56:30,922 --> 00:56:31,882
Mari, duduk sini.

623
00:56:36,768 --> 00:56:37,733
Fah masih tidur?

624
00:56:38,730 --> 00:56:41,914
Oh, dia dah bangun. Dia tengah mandi.

625
00:56:46,778 --> 00:56:47,216
Ya.

626
00:56:48,512 --> 00:56:50,032
- Silakan, sayang.
- Terima kasih.

627
00:56:53,109 --> 00:56:54,896
Dan Fun pula? Dia sihat?

628
00:56:57,573 --> 00:57:00,325
Betul, dah lama kita tak jumpa dia.

629
00:57:08,090 --> 00:57:10,901
- Selamat pagi.
- Selamat pagi, sayang.

630
00:57:13,530 --> 00:57:17,029
- Apa khabar?
- Kami baik.

631
00:57:17,973 --> 00:57:20,896
Kami mungkin akan pergi ke Phuket.

632
00:57:44,149 --> 00:57:46,789
Selamat tinggal.

633
00:57:50,864 --> 00:57:51,962
Datang selalu, ya?

634
00:57:52,272 --> 00:57:53,130
Ya, saya akan datang.

635
00:57:53,989 --> 00:57:54,928
Pandu hati-hati.

636
00:57:55,045 --> 00:57:55,749
Ya, ayah.

637
00:57:57,354 --> 00:57:58,309
Kami gerak dulu.

638
00:57:58,460 --> 00:58:01,520
- Selamat tinggal, mak dan ayah.
- Jaga diri elok-elok.

639
00:58:20,288 --> 00:58:21,098
Manisnya.

640
00:58:29,253 --> 00:58:30,368
Ada tempat nak singgah, Phoon?

641
00:58:38,389 --> 00:58:39,717
Kuil di kampung.

642
00:59:08,944 --> 00:59:09,408
Um...

643
00:59:11,445 --> 00:59:15,253
Kau tak nak tanya kenapa kita balik Phuket?

644
00:59:15,930 --> 00:59:17,322
Pelik ke kalau aku tak tanya?

645
00:59:19,136 --> 00:59:19,850
Pelik.

646
00:59:20,885 --> 00:59:23,765
Sekurang-kurangnya tanya lah.

647
00:59:29,216 --> 00:59:31,114
P'Fah mesti marah aku.

648
00:59:32,810 --> 00:59:33,882
Kenapa aku nak marah?

649
00:59:37,605 --> 00:59:39,386
Tak apa kalau kau marah aku.

650
00:59:40,170 --> 00:59:41,338
Aku akan minta maaf.

651
00:59:41,749 --> 00:59:42,640
Tapi...

652
00:59:44,784 --> 00:59:47,482
Boleh tak kita jangan putus?

653
00:59:48,794 --> 00:59:49,498
Phoon.

654
00:59:50,277 --> 00:59:53,056
Kita baru bercinta. Kenapa cakap pasal putus?

655
00:59:54,165 --> 00:59:55,232
Itu tak elok langsung.

656
00:59:55,504 --> 00:59:56,880
Patut aku “hukum” kau sebab tu?

657
00:59:58,282 --> 00:59:59,514
Aku serius.

658
01:00:00,320 --> 01:00:01,509
Kita takkan putus.

659
01:00:03,002 --> 01:00:05,205
Ya. Tak mungkin.

660
01:00:09,066 --> 01:00:10,597
Lama sangat baru dapat jumpa kau.

661
01:00:10,954 --> 01:00:12,240
P'Fah takkan lepaskan semudah tu.

662
01:00:18,389 --> 01:00:18,944
Jom.

663
01:01:00,650 --> 01:01:01,765
P'Fah.

664
01:01:02,213 --> 01:01:03,648
Maafkan aku.

665
01:01:05,173 --> 01:01:06,933
Tentang semuanya—

666
01:01:08,213 --> 01:01:09,370
aku tipu kau.

667
01:01:18,197 --> 01:01:18,949
Phoon.

668
01:01:20,256 --> 01:01:21,189
Tak apa.

669
01:01:21,733 --> 01:01:23,157
Aku dah tahu.

670
01:01:26,720 --> 01:01:28,032
Aku dah tahu lama.

671
01:01:29,013 --> 01:01:32,352
Aku cuma tunggu kau sedia beritahu sendiri.

672
01:01:36,896 --> 01:01:38,234
Kau tak marah aku?

673
01:01:39,626 --> 01:01:40,842
Aku faham kau.

674
01:02:00,997 --> 01:02:01,690
Fun.

675
01:02:02,357 --> 01:02:04,965
Maaf sebab aku tak pernah datang jumpa kau.

676
01:02:07,146 --> 01:02:08,880
Kau tak perlu risau pasal Phoon lagi.

677
01:02:10,213 --> 01:02:11,269
Mulai sekarang,

678
01:02:11,717 --> 01:02:13,088
aku akan jaga dia sendiri.

679
01:02:23,088 --> 01:02:24,133
Jangan menangis.

680
01:02:57,000 --> 01:02:57,840
Fun.

681
01:03:06,512 --> 01:03:09,477
Mungkin aku dah tak perlu risau apa-apa lagi.

682
01:03:10,789 --> 01:03:12,400
Memang dah sampai masa aku pergi sekarang.

683
01:03:18,304 --> 01:03:19,840
Tak boleh tinggal?

684
01:03:27,994 --> 01:03:30,240
Terima kasih untuk semuanya.

685
01:03:33,466 --> 01:03:34,000
Mm.

686
01:03:35,024 --> 01:03:36,460
Aku sayang kau, Fun.

687
01:03:40,106 --> 01:03:41,424
Aku pun sayang kau, Phoon.

688
01:04:06,357 --> 01:04:07,429
Kau okey?

689
01:04:20,794 --> 01:04:22,138
Aku boleh rasa Fun.

690
01:04:28,277 --> 01:04:29,605
Walaupun sakit,

691
01:04:29,861 --> 01:04:30,602
dan aku rindu dia,

692
01:04:33,024 --> 01:04:34,704
setiap kali aku rasa dia,

693
01:04:36,544 --> 01:04:38,336
rasa tu sangat menenangkan.

694
01:04:41,269 --> 01:04:42,368
Tapi kali ni,

695
01:04:49,322 --> 01:04:50,357
dia datang untuk ucap selamat tinggal.

696
01:04:53,818 --> 01:04:55,466
Sebab dia dah tak perlu risau lagi, kan?

697
01:04:59,962 --> 01:05:01,189
Aku faham.

698
01:05:02,912 --> 01:05:04,570
Aku nak Fun berehat dengan tenang.

699
01:05:05,877 --> 01:05:07,018
Dia tak perlu risau pasal aku lagi.

700
01:05:09,253 --> 01:05:10,677
Tapi bila aku fikir balik...

701
01:05:11,376 --> 01:05:12,460
aku ingat kita mungkin takkan jumpa lagi.

702
01:05:16,208 --> 01:05:17,013
Cuma...

703
01:05:18,389 --> 01:05:20,080
rasa pedih sikit.

704
01:05:27,141 --> 01:05:28,576
Phoon, dengar aku.

705
01:05:29,930 --> 01:05:31,274
Fun tak pergi mana-mana.

706
01:05:32,544 --> 01:05:33,376
Sebab Fun

707
01:05:34,837 --> 01:05:36,896
akan sentiasa hidup dalam ingatan kita berdua.

708
01:05:41,530 --> 01:05:42,298
Betul.

709
01:06:14,624 --> 01:06:17,642
Aku tak sangka dapat tengok matahari terbenam dengan kau.

710
01:06:19,733 --> 01:06:20,565
Kenapa pula?

711
01:06:25,568 --> 01:06:26,976
Rasa macam mustahil.

712
01:06:27,498 --> 01:06:29,077
Hah? Kenapa?

713
01:06:31,770 --> 01:06:32,981
Dulu,

714
01:06:33,312 --> 01:06:35,066
setiap kali aku tengok langit,

715
01:06:36,778 --> 01:06:38,400
aku selalu tanya diri aku

716
01:06:39,861 --> 01:06:41,765
sama ada P'Fah tengok langit yang sama.

717
01:06:44,869 --> 01:06:46,256
Tapi hari ni, aku dapat jawapannya.

718
01:06:47,786 --> 01:06:49,178
Kita memang tengok langit yang sama.

719
01:06:54,149 --> 01:06:56,016
Maksudnya kita tengok langit sama-sama.

720
01:08:09,018 --> 01:08:12,026
Phoon, kau nak tinggal sekali dengan aku?

721
01:08:12,730 --> 01:08:15,173
- Ya?
- Jangan fikir banyak.

722
01:08:15,456 --> 01:08:17,584
P'Fah yakin mak ayah kau akan faham.

723
01:08:18,069 --> 01:08:19,845
Aku dengar ada pelabur di Chiang Mai

724
01:08:20,037 --> 01:08:21,872
yang berminat nak bekerjasama dengan kita.

725
01:08:22,288 --> 01:08:23,669
Mereka nak bincang butiran dulu.

726
01:08:25,477 --> 01:08:27,520
Budak tak kenang budi, sia-sia semua yang aku bagi.

727
01:08:27,802 --> 01:08:30,106
Sepatutnya aku tak biar perempuan tu lahirkan kau.

728
01:08:30,160 --> 01:08:32,800
Ini akibat perbuatan kau—tanggunglah sikit.

729
01:08:32,906 --> 01:08:35,274
Jangan fikir kau kena hadap semua sorang-sorang lagi.

730
01:08:35,616 --> 01:08:37,136
Phoon, kau akan sentiasa ada aku.

